Quote:  In 1953 Pat Vincent kicked `into the box' and upset our fullback. This time Alan Clark, Don McIntosh and myself took turns at playing spare fullback. ... I remember hearing their captain ... say to Vincent `For goodness sake kick into the gap' and Vincent replied `I can't - they've blocked all the gaps!'
